<div id="c3">
<p>These actions are very much driven by human desires &#8212; social desires. Humans are social animals and want to look good in front of their peers. If you walk out of a restaurant without paying, you will look bad for breaking your promise. No one wants that, and everyone wants to look good in front of their peers.</p>

